126
00:07:42,839 --> 00:07:45,139
Pemandangan yang indah!

127
00:07:45,139 --> 00:07:48,839
Seolah kau bisa melihat Bumi itu bulat!

128
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:51,839
Ini lantai 30.

129
00:08:03,139 --> 00:08:05,239
Oh, Conan.

130
00:08:05,239 --> 00:08:07,039
